<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 27 at 6:27AM EST  by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>...A wintry mix early this morning near the Michigan border...
Snow mixed with rain at times from Coldwater to Hillsdale should
end by 9 AM EST. Light snow accumulations on roads may cause
slippery conditions. If you are traveling on roads in this area
including Highway 12 and Interstate 69, slow down and allow extra
time to reach your destination. Temperatures should rise several
degrees above freezing by late morning and improve any weather
related travel issues.</description>
